cs.CL, cs.DB, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR. 

The paper deals with natural language processing and database querying, which suggests it could belong to the categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), databases (cs.DB), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), and information retrieval (cs.IR). However, since the focus is on using deep neural networks and reinforcement learning to generate SQL queries from natural language, cs.CL and cs.DB are the most likely categories.
